quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  85,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  85,1,qasam hai mazboot qii'aon walay aasman ki
  85,2,aur uss din ki jis ka wada kya gaya hai
  85,3,aur dekhnay walay ki aur dekhi jaane wali cheez ki
  85,4,ke maaray gay garhay walay
  85,5,( uss garhay walay ) jis mein khoob bharkate hue eendhan ki aag thi
  85,6,jabkay woh uss garhay ke kinare baithy hue thay
  85,7,aur jo kuch woh imaan laane walon ke sath kar rahay thay ussay dekh rahay thay
  85,8,aur unn ahal imaan se unn ki dushmani iss ke siwa kisi wajah se nah thi ke woh uss khuda par imaan le aeye thay jo zabardast aur apni zaat mein aap Mahmood hai
  85,9,"jo asmano aur zameen ki saltanat ka maalik hai, aur woh khuda sab kuch dekh raha hai"
  85,10,"jin logon ne momin mardon aur aurton par zulm o sitam tora aur phir is se Taib nah hue, yaqeenan unn ke liye jahannum ka azaab hai aur un ke liye jalaaye jaane ki saza hai"
  85,11,"jo log imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye, yaqeenan unn ke liye jannat ke baagh hain jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi, yeh hai barri kamyabi"
  85,12,dar haqeeqat tumahray Rab ki pakar barri sakht hai
  85,13,wohi pehli baar peda karta hai aur wohi dobarah peda kere ga
  85,14,"aur woh bakhsnay wala hai, mohabbat karne wala hai"
  85,15,"arsh ka maalik hai, buzurag o bartar hai"
  85,16,aur jo kuch chahay kar daalnay wala hai
  85,17,kya tumhe lashkaron ki khabar pohanchi hai ?
  85,18,firaon aur samood ( ke lashkaron ) ki ?
  85,19,magar jinhon ne kufar kya hai woh jhutlanay mein lagey hue hain
  85,20,halaank Allah ne un ko ghairay mein le rakha hai
  85,21,( unn ke jhutlanay se iss quran ka kuch nahi bigartaa ) balkay yeh quran buland paya hai
  85,22,uss looh mein ( naqsh hai ) jo mehfooz hai
